{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Czpyoom2TXod5WT3stCAfh","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: schema-migration-safety\n     3→description: Generate two-step rollout-safe Django migrations plus model-field patching using jig.\n     4→---\n     5→\n     6→# Schema Migration Safety (Jig)\n     7→\n     8→Use this skill for backwards-compatible model field rollout.\n     9→\n    10→## Required Variables\n    11→\n    12→- `app_label`\n    13→- `model_name`\n    14→- `field_name`\n    15→- `field_type`\n    16→- `add_field_kwargs`\n    17→- `final_field_kwargs`\n    18→- `previous_migration`\n    19→- `add_migration_name`\n    20→- `finalize_migration_name`\n    21→- `backfill_value`\n    22→\n    23→## Usage\n    24→\n    25→```bash\n    26→jig run ${CLAUDE_SKILL_DIR}/recipe.yaml --vars '{\n    27→  \"app_label\": \"core\",\n    28→  \"model_name\": \"Entity\",\n    29→  \"field_name\": \"classification\",\n    30→  \"field_type\": \"models.CharField\",\n    31→  \"add_field_kwargs\": \"max_length=20, null=True\",\n    32→  \"final_field_kwargs\": \"max_length=20\",\n    33→  \"previous_migration\": \"0007_auto_20260407_1200\",\n    34→  \"add_migration_name\": \"0008_add_entity_classification\",\n    35→  \"finalize_migration_name\": \"0009_enforce_entity_classification\",\n    36→  \"backfill_value\": \"\\\"standard\\\"\"\n    37→}'\n    38→```\n    39→\n    40→## Notes\n    41→\n    42→- Migration 1 adds nullable field + backfill.\n    43→- Migration 2 enforces final constraints.\n    44→- `model_file` patching targets the first class in the file. Keep one primary model per file for this recipe.\n    45→- If jig fails, use rendered output from stderr and apply manually.\n    46→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it looks malicious. If it does, you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer high-level questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2747f7d-bfd1-435f-b873-89459d2727ec","uuid":"6195da75-269d-49eb-ac0a-7fe31c02aeaf"}
